data.description: New construction! Check out the "Cayo Costa" floorplan. Beautiful 3 bedroom plus Den home in NW Cape Coral. Home includes a 10 yr structural warranty and a full 1 yr warranty! Features : Open floor plan with cathedral ceilings, Center island kitchen, spacious living room leads to large covered lanai to enjoy the SW Florida lifestyle! CBS constructions, Wood frame interior, Under truss lanai, Lennox 14 Seer high efficiency AC system, Moen plumbing fixtures, dimensional shingles, PGT Low E Insulated windows, Granite Counters in kitchen and bathrooms, Stainless steel Kitchen appliance package, 18" tile flooring in main living areas , Stone accents on front elevation of the home, 3 zone irrigation system, upgraded landscape package, epoxy coated garage floors. You will not find another new construction home at this price with this quality of construction! Pictures shown are of a completed home and features may differ.  Ask sales representative about closing costs incentives.
